name: SamDoesArts Embedding (long Training)
description:
Here is hopefully my last embedding for the Artist SamDoesArts. I think i learned what i wanted from training with his style and time to move on to the next.

I leave you with the last embedding i trained and tested.

It is quite strong so you'll have to play with the embedding strength. I recomend between 0.82 and 0.87

modelVersions.name: V1
modelVersions.description: First release of the long trained Embedding
